text: Swiney is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *C. C. Swiney (born 1981), American writer, actor and comedian *Erwin Swiney (born 1978), American football player *Frances Swiney (1847–1922), British feminist, writer and theosophist *George Swiney (1793–1844), English physician and founder of the Swiney Prize *Tom Swiney (1875–1945), Australian politician ==See also== *Swiney Prize, awarded every five years for medical or general jurisprudence
title: Swiney (surname)
